{"tid":2352393,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"越秀交通基建(01052.HK)11月份旗下12個公路項目日均車流量升幅達雙位數","createTime":"2021-01-04T04:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T04:12:35.000Z","uid":215603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"08a83660b4f90b831907a62c72e1f711e6252c15","tid":2352393,"uid":215603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:12:35.000Z","msg":"越秀交通基建(<a href=\"http://01052.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01052.HK&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZybktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=9cd1c8a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01052.HK</a>)11月份旗下12個公路項目日均車流量升幅達雙位數<br />\n<br />\n越秀交通基建公布，11月份旗下公路項目有達12個項目的日均車流量升幅達雙位數，其中廣西蒼郁高速日均車流量增幅接近80%，路費收入增加39%。"}]}